headline: Raymond James announces inaugural Ready for School cohort, committing over $7.5 million to nonprofits supporting local students
summary: The program, designed to help students prepare for brighter futures inside, outside and beyond the classroom, will award over $2.5 million annually for three years to 11 Tampa Bay organizations.ST....
